  "texts": [
    "Model: The original pre-trained weights of the LLM are removed and the weights for all layers are randomly initialized.",
    "Layer Freezing: Except for the weights at layer l, all other weights for the subsequent layers of an LLM are frozen to isolate the training to one layer at a time.",
    "Training is completed on the task dataset with the l-th layer unfrozen.",
    "This is achieved by maximizing the conditional language modeling objective:",
    "where x i and y i are sequences of tokens and T l i ∈ ℜ n×n is the matrix for task i at the l-th layer and n × n the dimensions of the original pre-trained weight matrix."
  ],
